Supplementary Data README

This submission includes six supplementary data files:

- Supplementary_Data_01_harmonized_phenotype_data.csv
- Supplementary_Data_02_study_metadata.csv
- Supplementary_Data_03_observation_summary.csv
- Supplementary_Data_04_model_comparison.csv
- Supplementary_Data_05_epistasis_matrix.csv
- Supplementary_Data_06_mutation_classifications.csv

All files are derived from publicly available data sources and processed analysis outputs reported in the manuscript.
